                "name": "Dressor",
                "description": "Holds clothes. Putting clothes on top will put them inside.\r\n\r\nDirty clothes are recognized and transported through a cutout in the wall to a small lift that goes down to the machine machine room. To do this, a flap falls forward from the wall, forming a chute. On the return route, the flap can raise straight up instead.",
