            {
                "id": 13,
                "name": "Sink",
                "description": "A full array of cosmetic treatment options, including a machine that trims, plucks, cuts, and styles hair.\r\n\r\nDental care not only includes toothbrushes and floss but also fluoride and a water drill on a robotic arm, along with a scanner to determine what needs to be done.\r\n\r\nA wide mirror in front has vents and water spot removers, so it's ready to view immediately when you get out of the tub.",
